BRIDGE BUILDING
===============

Bridges let you cross water, connecting your empire across seas.

COMMANDS
--------
  build b SECT DIR     Build a bridge span from SECT in direction DIR
  build t SECT DIR     Build a bridge tower from SECT in direction DIR

DIRECTIONS
----------
  NE  (or ne)    North-East
  E   (or e)     East
  SE  (or se)    South-East
  SW  (or sw)    South-West
  W   (or w)     West
  NW  (or nw)    North-West

SECTOR TYPES
------------
  #   Bridge Head  — terminus; owned land sector adjacent to water.
                     Designate a land sector as # before bridging.
  =   Bridge Span  — the bridge crossing water between heads/towers.
  @   Bridge Tower — mid-ocean support tower; built from a span
                     into deep water to extend the bridge further.

BRIDGE SPAN (build b)
---------------------
  Source:     Any owned # (Bridge Head) or @ (Bridge Tower) sector
              at ≥60% efficiency.
  Target:     The adjacent water sector in the chosen direction.
              It must have bridge support (an adjacent # or @ sector
              at ≥60% that is not the source itself).
  Tech req:   10
  Materials:  100 HCM from the source sector
  Cost:       $1,000 from your treasury

  The new = sector is created at 10% efficiency, owned by you.

BRIDGE TOWER (build t)
----------------------
  Source:     Any owned = (Bridge Span) sector at ≥60% efficiency.
  Target:     An adjacent water sector in the chosen direction.
              The target must NOT be adjacent to any land sector
              (towers extend into open water only).
  Tech req:   100
  Materials:  300 HCM from the source sector
  Cost:       $3,000 from your treasury

  The new @ sector is created at 10% efficiency, owned by you.

BRIDGE SUPPORT
--------------
  A water sector can receive a span only when it has "support" —
  at least one adjacent # or @ sector at ≥60% efficiency.  This
  prevents dangling spans that have nothing to anchor to.

TIPS
----
  • Designate your coastal sector as # first (e.g.: des 4,4 #).
  • Raise its efficiency to 60% before building.
  • Bridge spans and towers grow toward 100% efficiency on update
    like any other sector.
  • To cross a wide ocean, build a tower mid-span and continue
    from there with another span.
  • Bridges can be conquered like any sector.

